ding subtitle=\"Lady of Music; Change Queen; Bards\' Muse\"]Despia[/heading][vc_column_text]The Goddess of creativity and joyous change; Despia\'s abilities center around the ability to change the world in ways both large and small.\r\n\r\nShe is awakened by changes made in the world, and is known to have been especially kind to those who work to make positive change in the world, and so is also known to be a giver of small gifts and presents.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_text_separator title=\"Gains 1XP per Dollar Donated to Charity\"][fancy-ul icon_type=\"standard_dash\" color=\"Accent-Color\"]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Level 0: 0XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Audience gets to vote on a change which the GM will implement.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Level 1: 10XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>2nd vote</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Level 2: 50XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>3rd vote</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Level 3: 110XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Make one major change to each of the characters.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Level 4: 190XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>CHALLENGE ACCEPTED TKS Will match all donations made to this point, and donate it to Extra Life on behalf of Critical Role.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Level 5: 290XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>4th vote</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Level 6: 410XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>5th vote</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Level 7: 550XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Gives away a Promotional Pack which will include a DCC rulebook signed by the GM with an insert signed by the players.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Level 8: 710XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Ability ???</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Level 9: 890XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Ability ???</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Level 10: 1090XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Ability ???</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/fancy-ul][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding=\"no-extra-padding\" column_padding_position=\"all\" background_color_opacity=\"1\" background_hover_color_opacity=\"1\" width=\"1/3\"][heading subtitle=\"The Watcher; Applause Maker; Fear Banisher\"]Grandiok[/heading][vc