r\n	<li>Grandiok\'s XP will count for double!!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Level 9: 890XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Our writers will produce an entire DCC module influenced by audience suggestions</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Level 10: 1090XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><em>Ability <em>???</em></em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/fancy-ul][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row type=\"in_container\" scene_position=\"center\" text_color=\"dark\" text_align=\"left\" overlay_strength=\"0.3\"][vc_column column_padding=\"no-extra-padding\" column_padding_position=\"all\" background_color_opacity=\"1\" background_hover_color_opacity=\"1\" width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]This progression is in flux and may change up until the show begins, and mystery unlocks will be revealed as they are approached.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]','The Keep Studios Presents: Audience Character Advancement','','inherit','closed','closed','','143-revision-v1','','','2016-02-04 16:47:02','2016-02-04 16:47:02','',143,'http://thekeepstudios.com/2016/02/04/143-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(200,9,'2016-05-05 02:53:29','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Meet the Team','','draft','closed','closed','','','','','2016-05-05 02:53:29','2016-05-05 02:53:29','',0,'http://thekeepstudios.com/?page_id=200',0,'page','',0),(201,9,'2016-05-05 02:53:29','2016-05-05 02:53:29','','Meet the Team','','inherit','closed','closed','','200-revision-v1','','','2016-05-05 02:53:29','2016-05-05 02:53:29','',200,'http://thekeepstudios.com/2016/05/05/200-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(202,3,'2016-10-02 18:47:54','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','open','open','','','','','2016-10-02 18:47:54','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://thekeepstudios.com/?p=202',0,'post','',0),(203,3,'2016-10-02 18:48:34','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Viventure Game Jam','','draft','open','open','','','','','2016-10-02 18:48:34','2016-10-02 18:48:34','',0,'http://thekeepstudios.com/?p=203',0,'post','',0),(204,6,'2017-04-06 23:00:08','0000-00-00 00:00:00